57 Earth pet with Bo4+muzzle+DS, elemental blanket and summoned armor.<br>
<br>
I was at 60% hp, 25% mana when done.<br>
Pet was at 20% hp<br>
<br>
Very close fight, chain-casting shock of swords as fast as I could (thank you focus items).  Was afraid to use Sirrocco with me standing underneath him.  I tried to pull him down, but instead of swimming towards me, he cast a spell (resisted) and pet swims up to attack him up top.<br>
<br>
Was quite the scare.  Very good chance of (A) dying, (B) Undertow going into a wall and poofing, (C) something coming by too close and aggroing on me.  However, (D) I win and loot the blazing wand. <p><DIV style="position:relative; width=80%; filter:glow(color=FF0000)"><a style="font-weight:bold; color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration: none" href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796  target="new-window">Zacatac Soulwanderer</a></div>
